{"tid":1513167,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[眾籌] 抗爭專用遙控器 抵制TVB","createTime":"2019-08-28T08:09:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T10:31:36.000Z","uid":291805,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"992f3d02b8ea822528023c59a39daca0ed20c9a8","tid":1513167,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:09:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/giGFNR6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgiGFNR6.jpg&h=d0bbc84d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌網頁:</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%e5%91%bd%e9%81%8b%e8%87%aa%e9%81%b8%e9%81%99%e6%8e%a7%e5%99%a8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25e5%2591%25bd%25e9%2581%258b%25e8%2587%25aa%25e9%2581%25b8%25e9%2581%2599%25e6%258e%25a7%25e5%2599%25a8%2F&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5PZItop%2BIuorIKtd308SUMA%3D&h=a8c787cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%e5%91%bd%e9%81%8b%e8%87%aa%e9%81%b8%e9%81%99%e6%8e%a7%e5%99%a8/</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">原post: </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1320101/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1320101/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nTVB報導偏頗，不盡不實，屢次抹黑反送中示威活動，出賣香港市民。<br />\n在此<span style=\"color: red;\">呼籲全港18區抗爭者，合力將所有酒樓，茶餐廳，醫院，護老院，健身室等公共空間的電視轉台。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/937USiT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F937USiT.jpg&h=f05ad7a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">由TVB 81/82/83/84/85 轉去 港台 31/32，開電視 77 或 Viu TV 99台。</span><br />\n<br />\n小弟對萬用遙控略有認識，在過去一個月，與工廠開發了一款<span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭專用遙控器</span> (universal remote)。<br />\n<br />\n產品可控制<span style=\"color: red;\">9大電視品牌 + 1個自選品牌</span>，於出廠時已預設轉台及其他基本功能。 簡易操作如下：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 查看電視品牌<br />\n<br />\n2. 按鍵選擇該品牌<br />\n<br />\n3. 按CH+-鍵轉台<br />\n<br />\n現眾籌HKD120000，當中已包括開發和測試費用，4000件大貨，4%眾籌平台手續費，運輸到全港18區和18區智能櫃費用。<br />\n</span><br />\n如眾籌達標，將隨即下訂單，預計約30天內交貨。<br />\n<br />\n請捐款者screen cap捐款成功畫面，email到freehkremote@gmail.com，告知希望取貨的地區。<br />\n<br />\n當貨到香港，我將以捐款者的email聯絡，告知所屬地區的取貨密碼和地址。<br />\n<br />\n這次眾籌屬個人自發，沒有人手，故只能用<span style=\"color: red;\">honour system，煩請捐$50者自取一件，$100者自取兩件，如此類推。 由於智能櫃有時間限制，請於通知發出後40小時內取貨。 由於無法控制參與者是否全部自律，恕不能保證捐款者一定能取得產品，只能做到盡量安排，先到先得。</span><br />\n<br />\n眾籌目的，不像Kickstarter或Indiegogo買產品，而是要<span style=\"color: red;\">令更多的香港抗爭者加入全港轉台行列</span>。<br />\n<br />\n多謝支持！！ <span style=\"color: red;\">香港人加油！！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">以下是樣板實物圖: </span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jpMOcj8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjpMOcj8.jpg&h=ff693a58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HS5fBUG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHS5fBUG.jpg&h=2627039f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">以下是說明書:</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zK2RaeU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzK2RaeU.png&h=a7e86169&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6zTT71z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6zTT71z.png&h=8273a63b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BjaZ3zV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBjaZ3zV.png&h=e0be1c14&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">以下是code list:</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">紅色</span>為主要品牌，是出廠<span style=\"color: red;\">default setup</span><br />\n有需要時，其他品牌可自行利用OTH鍵setup (產品實際上支援超過500個品牌，篇幅所限我只節錄約30個在本港較常見的品牌。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JQPLY8f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJQPLY8f.png&h=49f4c808&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bde033330713da074a9e215da3878cc941ffe923","tid":1513167,"uid":284522,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"