"tid":1513167,"uid":57633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73633dc4a7b6709f962633b8018cbc572c850010","tid":1513167,"uid":57633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:03:01.000Z","msg":"咁大個撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且咁多制<br />\n方死人睇唔到係我搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n提議你淨係整一個制既發射器<br />\n轉咩台呢d settle野就一早用電話apps到set<br />\n最好小巧到個餐廳伙記企我隔離都唔知係我轉台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:04:38.000Z","msg":"不過講又咁講<br />\n其他台都無24 news<br />\n轉過去一陣<br />\n咪又會比人轉返去cctbb既24新聞台"},{"pid":"47b3c4b49d64f52b6a4d02e46290b334cd79ec6e","tid":1513167,"uid":66547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:07:36.000Z","msg":"用有紅外線電話就OK，遙控器咁招搖"},{"pid":"9adb1cae8907100a5d42f3eb2174550e13d6c226","tid":1513167,"uid":27432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:09:09.000Z","msg":"買粒紅外線插落電話<br />\n搞撚掂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3670a651413eee66d51fb737c11e9671d089fe11","tid":1513167,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:19:16.000Z","msg":"我都同意細係最好的，但電話多數本身係冇紅外。<br />\n有啲Android電話仲有3.5mm，有啲得返個USB-C。<br />\nApple就Lightning，就咁睇已經有3種唔同既IR adapter。<br />\n去邊度買？　用咩app?　每次見唔同brand setup一次?<br />\n我整呢個remote都係想簡單直接，人人都識用，冇兼容性問題。<br />\n係就係大啲，無可否認係缺點。"},{"pid":"db2d2042836842b563f329b5bdc9c9fc5707ab1a","tid":1513167,"uid":52577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:22:07.000Z","msg":"樓主真係收返成本價啦<br />\n$30都話吸血？咁你自己唔去整埋一份吸下？"},{"pid":"81c2146137220fa578bd83674b29d59524c4c2cb","tid":1513167,"uid":185731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:31:36.000Z","msg":"有心機 不過size 太大"}]}